summary: This is an overhaul of my Layla mod, she is available in either Blonde or Brunette, Auto-Level or Calculated and Essential or Non-Essential. She is a Ranger/Scout type character that will primarily use the bow but will also take the sword should danger come too close. She is located in Whiterun at The Bannared Mare.
